{"tid":1401663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅色分化警號！紅色分化警號！","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:53:11.000Z","uid":19085,"like":157,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"a36de2d2acb0c69635965bb3c74428c56b670190","tid":1401663,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:29.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">如果你唔係三毛，但認為前線今日表現好差</span></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n屌鳩前線，對件事絕對無幫助！我明白大家都係痛心佢地被捕，我好明白。但都請大家控制下自己，盡量留constructive 嘅comment instead of destructive. <br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你唔係三毛，但覺得前線有鬼</span></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n作為一個前線，成日都聽到好多好戇鳩嘅提議。但大多數情況，前線嘅人有足夠嘅判斷能力。我唔排除有鬼，但佢地嘅影響力其實唔會好大。今日我唔起到，我唔知。如果巴絲們真係擔心嘅，請下次加入前線，幫手俾意見同討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">如果你係三毛分化撚</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n我勸你地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>慳啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"04375b83b743b3949aeadb980ad081d397724b46","tid":1401663,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"1d4bc9bde91ab7a879e48f1573be0d5c285af92f","tid":1401663,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04375b83b743b3949aeadb980ad081d397724b46","tid":1401663,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"98bcc3b63835f00109d28c14bc265c58dbcffdaa","tid":1401663,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d4bc9bde91ab7a879e48f1573be0d5c285af92f","tid":1401663,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04375b83b743b3949aeadb980ad081d397724b46","tid":1401663,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2